  description="A quantum link is bounded by two impairments: channel loss (which HEG fights with heralding + retries) and qubit errors as fidelity + decoherence (which HEP fights with purification). Grounded in fibre 0.20 dB/km, hollow-core 0.091 dB/km, free-space and satellite numbers, memory T₂ across platforms, and Bell-pair fidelity thresholds. Worked through one 200 km link budget end-to-end."
